main_body:
Regulation (EC) No 1216/2003 is hereby amended as follows:
1. ‘NACE Rev. 1’ is replaced by ‘NACE Rev. 2’ throughout the text and the Annexes;
2. ‘Sections L, M, N and O’ are replaced by ‘Sections O to S’ in Article 4 and in Annex IV;
3. ‘Sections C to K’ are replaced by ‘Sections B to N’ in Annex IV.
